name: Googy Goo
description:
Description:

Your spaceship has been invaded by aliens only known as Googy Goos.  Survive as long as you can before they completely take over.

Controls:

Arrow Keys - Move

Space - Shoot Blaster

Items:

Red Blaster Symbol  - Grab Blaster

Ammo Computer - Grab Ammo

Enemies:

Googy Goo (yellow) - The weakest but most populous Googy Goo.

Strong Googy Goo (pink) - Deals extra damage, but is also slower than the Googy Goo.

Fast Googy Goo (blue) - Quick and agile, but deals less damage.

Googy Goo Queen (gray) - Deals the most damage and is the fastest, but can easily be taken out with a blaster.

Notes:

This game will be completed soon, but I don't have particularly big plans for it.
